&lt;p&gt;Our technology is built with full stack JS (Node/Express), with infrastructure managed by Terraform and Ansible, and runs on AWS 24/7 365.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring in the United States and Canada to work fully remotely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The salary range for this role is $100-150k, and could increase beyond that commensurate with experience.&lt;/p&gt;
