&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re growing quickly and are scaling up. As&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Forward Deployed Engineer, &lt;/strong&gt;you&#39;ll ensure that Canopy Connect’s API customers launch with our product quickly and successfully. This position requires strong technical and communication skills. You will work with companies that range from small startups to large technology unicorns.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
