&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead end-to-end API onboarding and implementation for new customers, guiding technical teams through setup, testing, and go-live.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as primary post-sale contact for strategic enterprise accounts, managing cross-functional relationships across product, engineering, and executive teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as an internal advocate for customer needs, providing structured feedback to product and engineering to inform roadmap priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze usage data to identify expansion opportunities and ensure customers realize measurable value from Canopy Connect’s platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support contract renewals and growth initiatives in partnership with Sales, Engineering and Leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
