&lt;li&gt;Strong technical acumen and ability to troubleshoot issues related to APIs, data integrations, and authentication workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills with the ability to translate technical concepts for non-technical stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience collaborating closely with engineering and product teams to deliver customer-driven solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of UX principles, workflow optimization, and data security protocols&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
